# Link Formatting Rules

## Link Structure
- **Format**: `[Display Text](URL "Tooltip")`
- **Consistency**: Use consistent link text across all documents
- **Accessibility**: Include descriptive tooltips for screen readers
- **Validation**: Verify all links are working and current

## External Links
- **Official sources**: Always link to official Romanian government websites
- **Language**: Prefer Romanian versions of official sites when available
- **Backup**: Include alternative links when possible
- **Status**: Mark links as "Last checked: [date]"

## Internal Links
- **Structure**: Use relative paths for internal documents
- **Anchors**: Link to specific sections using `#section-id`
- **Cross-references**: Link between related documents
- **Navigation**: Include table of contents with internal links

## Romanian Government Links
- **IGI**: https://igi.mai.gov.ro
- **ANAF**: https://www.anaf.ro
- **CNAS**: https://www.cnas.ro
- **Government Portal**: https://www.gov.ro
- **VIES**: https://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/vies/

## Link Categories
- **Official**: Government websites and forms
- **Reference**: Legal documents and regulations
- **Tools**: Online calculators and services
- **Support**: Help and contact information

## Link Maintenance
- **Regular checks**: Verify links monthly
- **Updates**: Update links when URLs change
- **Archives**: Archive old links with dates
- **Alternatives**: Provide backup links when possible

## Formatting Examples
```markdown
[IGI - Immigration](https://igi.mai.gov.ro "Official immigration website")
[ANAF - Tax Office](https://www.anaf.ro "Official tax administration")
[CNAS - Health Insurance](https://www.cnas.ro "National health insurance")
```

## Link Validation
- **Automated**: Use tools to check link validity
- **Manual**: Regular manual verification
- **User feedback**: Report broken links
- **Updates**: Fix broken links immediately

